dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Tiled DEM for Waushara County, WI 2017
dc_description_s: This data represents a LiDAR-derived tiled Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2017. A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features. This dataset contains individual files available for download consisting of smaller tiled geographic areas over the extent of an entire county.
uw_supplemental_s: This data is also available as a series of tiles to enable downloads of smaller, more specific areas within the county. To access the tiled data, please visit: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/scoapps/lidar/tile-search/?layer=waushara
